{
  "stem": "8753.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after they left, my sister says, you want me to marry those [NON-ENGLISH], those [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Only because they wore boots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I mean, she didn't talk to them to find out how intelligent they are.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it just meant a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in terms of the Jews in the town, in terms of professions, what were the similarities and differences between the townspeople that were not Jewish and the Jewish townspeople?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most non-Jewish people, the Polish and Ukrainians, were farmers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a shoemaker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a dressmaker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Jewish people had stores.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had grocery stores.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was one man, he sold leather, and also a grocer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like, that one room, one corner was a grocery store, six shelves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at another table he sold leather.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he sold cigarettes, which you had to have a permit or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he was called the rich man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I made a painting of him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have many paintings of this-- the life there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was a bit of a difference.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Although, there was also-- they called it a cooperative store, a grocery run by the government, I believe, for the town, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did they keep the prices at a certain-- what was-- what did it mean to be cooperative?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was just run by the townspeople.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was part of the government.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of the government, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I believe so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he raised potatoes, and corn, wheat, and [NON-ENGLISH], you know, what you call--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Groats.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oats.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oats.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Groats.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Groats.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Groats.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And oats, also, for the animals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used it mostly for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We made flour.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father would take the wheat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, of course, the people would cut the wheat in the fields and bring it to the barn.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
